title: David Lapham - Stray Bullets 1-40 Amy Racecar 1-2
description:
Note: For more than a month I wasn't able to upload .torrent files to TPB.
Now that I am, I'll be uploading my other comic torrents here, hope you like 'em.


Stray Bullets is a creator owned series written and drawn by David Lapham.
These series are black & white.
Amy Racecar are two spin-off specials from the series.
This two specials were colored by Sarah Dyer.
